text.tspan: The aim of the workshop is to prepare the next generation of mathematicians to boldly go where no

tspan.tspan: one has gone before by showing them research frontiers in mathematics in a tangible and
comprehensible way. It should reveal to students various possibilities for their research careers, both
in terms of future research opportunities and the choice of potential thesis or postdoctoral advisors.
